# Deck builder: card images over names

Where possible, use **Scryfall card images** for pickers, queues, selection, and swap UIs — not card-name lists.

## Prefer

- `CardTile`, swap `MiniCard`, or equivalent image tiles via `cardImageUrl`
- Names as `alt` text, image-load fallbacks, or tooltips only

## Avoid

- Name-only `<select>` / text lists for choosing cards when an image affordance can work
- Introducing name-primary edit flows that diverge from the visual swap queue

## Exception

Explicit list/name layouts (or a future list view mode) may use card names as the primary display. Filters that narrow an image grid by name are fine as auxiliary controls.
